channel.description:
Well, Zzzzzzzz(or w.e) requested the 'wooden sword' to be made, so here it is: *NOTE: its only named 'Wooden Sword' because of the all-wood handle+hilt.
[IMG]http://i369.photobucket.com/albums/oo131/0xXDylanXx0/WSword.jpg[/img] i didnt add anything fancy. i just kept it as it was intended to look. the blade in the render looks longer than it is in proportion to the handle. you'll need to resize the whole item to fit the hand, and for a drop model.
Download: http://www.mediafire.com/file/hyzdimzzzwm/ Enjoy.
